sql:
SELECT AVG(percentage_met_exceeded) AS average_percentage
FROM performance_metrics
WHERE grade_id = (SELECT grade_id FROM grades WHERE grade_name = '3rd Grade');

external_knowledge:
A high average percentage met or exceeded indicates strong performance in the subject;
A 3rd Grade corresponds to 8-9 years old students, typically in elementary school;
California is a state in the United States with a large and diverse student population.
